{
  "stem": "23428.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We looked exactly like the pictures in newspapers about the Russian partisans, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And actually, we start laughing, because here were these spoiled high school kids, some-- converted by pure theatrical means into-- into 'the criminal class,' in quotes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "199812.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think my brother was 199813.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I should say it has no A or B, which has exactly the same meaning as the-- the red triangle I had talked about.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anybody who was a transport Jude got an A or B in front of his number.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when it came to selection later, I think that was important, because obviously everybody looked at your tattoo.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] well, the only other-- the only other thing I remember from that introduction to Auschwitz, other than the theatrical side and being shorn and so on, deloused, was that we looked out of a window and saw two or three SS men with cattle whips [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] chasing a prisoner along the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I think this incident and the one in the prison that I told you about are probably the only two incidences of brutality of that sort that I do remember.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it made a profound impression on us to see this poor guy chased with the cattle whips.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The next thing was again a truck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we ended up-- now, the structure of Auschwitz, I can show you plans of it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it consists of-- of rectangular units, you know, maybe 20 of them, 30 of them, one next to the other, separated by barbed wire, and also separated by turrets, guard turrets with machine guns.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
